{"tid":2296510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如下屆區選投返民建聯 新民黨 工聯會 好無? 原來經過左一年 大家諗野仲係咁表面","createTime":"2020-11-22T13:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T16:38:34.000Z","uid":334720,"like":40,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1f332cdead87dbbef6a3f0968dbcad210ba3d9c1","tid":2296510,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"見到有po&nbsp;d人係咁屌區議員唔做野&nbsp;唔報告&nbsp;點點點<br />\n仲要有人用呢個point:&nbsp;派餅呢D民生野做得少過民賤聯點解要選佢地&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先呢,&nbsp;我就唔否認有人係白逗人工同9hea既&nbsp;<br />\n同埋奶共派班賤人全部都好努力, 無9hea既&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且d人選完9hea&nbsp;vs 奶共狗選完圍內利益輸送 + 再日日出黎用議員名義支持警察<br />\n你接受邊個多D?<br />\n<br />\n不如諗下自己當初點解要選佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當時根本就係投非建制<br />\n正如陳梓為咁,&nbsp;你地又笑人弱智笑人ON9笑人柒,&nbsp;預左佢唔做野添, 最後咪又係選出黎<br />\n<br />\n知唔知政府出左幾撚多力去全方位打壓佢地&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知唔知有D區議員連區選d錢&nbsp;政府都未撚找數&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記唔記得班奶共建制又比政府安排左其他民生工作,&nbsp;去架空區議會&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知唔知勁多警犬同藍絲不斷繼續阻礙緊D區議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp; 得閒走去check下佢地etc&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />接受到區議員d職位比建制派拎黎搵錢&nbsp;等佢地自己圍內派餅<br />\n反而就接受唔到部份區議員9hea&nbsp;白逗人工,&nbsp;明明人地都有呢D情況<br />\n所以呢個現象都幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一屆咁多素人,&nbsp;又多人自己solo出黎選,&nbsp;無另外自己組隊,&nbsp;<br />\n你就預人地又要做到野<br />\n又話要解決你巴士排隊問題&nbsp;點點點 完全偏離哂一開始選佢地既意義&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪選左民賤聯就搞得掂?&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你地去馬啦&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:&nbsp;由年頭開始就對區議會無期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;次次拉其他部門開會&nbsp;d乜撚野民政署拉隊走人<br />\n不斷打壓,&nbsp;唔係仲覺得區議會有幾大力量呀嘛<br />\n你地真係未撚訓醒<br />\n咁下屆你地出黎選啦屌你老母&nbsp;<br />\n如果我2023仲在生既話&nbsp;我實屌撚柒你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a62eb6d32cfaf3dd6434414e4f4966296efd88d","tid":2296510,"uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"民賤聯咁多人組隊<br />\n又咁多水<br />\n咁多餅派<br />\n下屆一票不投民主派啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e00e0b9a52af2bff3216c5ba96099d8940a2967","tid":2296510,"uid":334720,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"做野仲少過民賤聯,&nbsp;點解要選你?&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj